{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_51_01_short",
  "title": "小美山愛 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁぁ……どうしよう……",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "愛、どうしたの？　ため息なんてついて\nこころにまたイタズラされた？",
      "startTime": 8.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、イタズラはされていないんですが……『ミラクル\n☆アイドルバースデー！』のお仕事について悩んでて",
      "startTime": 14.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……！　愛ちゃんにも、お話が来たんだね\nでも、悩みって……？",
      "startTime": 22.3747785568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "誕生日に合わせて、なんでも願いを叶えてくれる\nっていう企画なんでしょ？　そんなに悩むことある？",
      "startTime": 28.6000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "お話をもらえたのは嬉しいんですが、集中出来なくて\n……実は、私の実家が一世一代のピンチなんです",
      "startTime": 38.0333344777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　愛ちゃんの実家って\nラーメン屋さんだったよね？　何があったの？",
      "startTime": 45.4999970754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "最近、実家の近所にラーメンの有名チェーン店が出来て\nうちからお客さんが離れちゃったんです",
      "startTime": 54.4333304088,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}